Just standing in front of a man puts you into mating mode
automatically, doesn't it?

\nc<Executive Officer>Sigh, I'm very eager to enjoy myself right now... but
unfortunately, this time it's really about business.

\nc<Executive Officer>We need to entertain a foreign client, but there's no
suitable employee available. I want you to take care of this
job.

\nc<Executive Officer>You are one of the top five women I've ever met when it
comes to your... talents. I'm sure the client will be
satisfied.

\nc<Executive Officer>The client is quite a maniac, so make sure you prepare
thoroughly. Heh. I'll leave the schedule adjustment to you.
\nc<Executive Officer>Work hard to make sure you don't fail.

\nc<Executive Officer>Since it's quite a maniacal client, make sure to prepare
thoroughly. Hehe. Then, I'll leave the schedule adjustments
to you.
